OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774123873
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show gnome ban lifted
OL,4,Cto encourage 'curiosity'
OL,6,FGnomes will be making an appearance at
OL,7,Fthe world-famous Chelsea Flower Show,
OL,8,Fas organisers lift their "gnome ban"
OL,9,Ffor the first time in over a decade.
OL,11,FThe Royal Horticultural Society (RHS),
OL,12,Fwhich organises the event, said it was
OL,13,Feven inviting celebrities to decorate
OL,14,Fgnomes to feature in this year's show.
OL,16,FThe final gnomes will then be
OL,17,Fauctioned off to raise funds for the
OL,18,Fcharity's campaign for school
OL,19,Fgardening.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
