PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774123873
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show gnome ban lifted
OL,4,Cto encourage 'curiosity'
OL,6,FGnomes were banned in 1990, to
OL,7,Fapparently prevent the show from
OL,8,Fbecoming too tacky, and have only
OL,9,Freturned once since, to mark the
OL,10,Fshow's centenary in 2013.
OL,12,FRTS Director General Clare Matterson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We've never needed the joy of
OL,14,Fgardening, the power of plants for our
OL,15,Fplanet or the peace of simply sitting
OL,16,Fin a garden, more".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1774123873
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show gnome ban lifted
OL,4,Cto encourage 'curiosity'
OL,6,FShe added: "We also want people to be
OL,7,Fplayful with their gardening, which is
OL,8,Fwhy we're lifting the gnome ban for
OL,9,Fthese celebrity gnomes, who will then,
OL,10,Fby being auctioned off, help us do
OL,11,Feven more to awaken a curiosity in
OL,12,Fgardening in school children and
OL,13,Fsupport our national campaign for
OL,14,Fschool gardening."
OL,16,FThis year, a gnome or two could even
OL,17,Fappear at the RHS and The King's
OL,18,FFoundation Curious Garden, which aims
OL,19,Fto spark curiosity and to inspire the
OL,20,Fnext generation of gardeners.
OL,26,@nD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
